Roma have made an enquiry to take defender Mapou Yanga-Mbiwa from Newcastle.

The France international - who arrived at St James' Park with a big reputation in January 2013 - also has an offer on the table from Marseille.

Yanga-Mbiwa, 25, captained Montpellier to the French title in 2011-12 but has failed to live up to his reputation in England. 

