He is yet to play for Newcastle this season with Mike Williamson and captain Fabricio Coloccini boss Alan Pardew's preferred central defensive partnership. 

Yanga-Mbiwa has made 46 appearances in all competitions for the Magpies and has been capped three times by France.  

